item.title: Cable Indstry Bangladesh
item.description: Bangladesh is one of the most growing GDP country in Southeast Asian region. According to wiki information, in 2020, Bangladesh’s GDP per capita income is estimated as per IMF data at US $5,139 (PPP) and US$2,064 (nominal). According to Trading Economics global macro models and analyst, the Bangladesh GDP is projected to trend around 310.00 USD Billion in 2021 and 340.00 USD Billion in 2022, according to our econometric models.
